headline.main: PRESIDENT'S VIEWS ENDORSED BY EDEN; Tells Press in Ottawa United Nations Are '95 Per Cent' Agreed on Principles

lead_paragraph: OTTAWA, March 31 -- Endorsement of President Roosevelt's statement yesterday that the United Nations were "about 95 per cent together" on the broad principles to be followed in current and post-war planning was given here today by British Foreign Secretary Anthony Eden at an hour's press conference in the Parliament Buildings.
